title: A NEW ERA: Ego Death & Grieving Your Past Self
description:
Join Camo as they welcome in a new season, updating “the girls” on the past few weeks away from the show. Camo is in a state of “metamorphosis,” grieving old versions of themself, find out what their ego death journey has been like and stay tuned for a Q&A at the end! 
Get 10% off your first month at BetterHelp.com/unfazed.
Get 50% off your first Care/Of order at TakeCareOf.com and enter code "unfazed50".
